# Employee Salary Prediction using Machine Learning

This project uses **Linear Regression** to predict employee salaries based on various inputs like experience, test score, and interview score. The app is built using **Streamlit** and trained in **Jupyter Notebook**.

---

## ğŸ’¡ Features

* Predicts salary based on input values:

  * Years of Experience
  * Test Score
  * Interview Score
* Model trained using Linear Regression
* Web app created using Streamlit
* Clean UI for real-time salary predictions


